column2:
"Great job!
It seems like the floating feeling is
still in me!"

"But I feel so relieved coming back to
this floor with no height difference."

"Since I'm feeling rather relaxed, why
don't we spend some time to think
about the plan for the next session?"
"I'll call you soon! Bye for now!"

"おつかれさまー！
まだなんか浮かんでるみたいな感じ！"

"でも高低差のないフロアに
戻ってくると、やっぱり落ち着くよー。"

"せっかくだから今日は落ち着いて
ゆっくり今後の訓練プランでも
考えてみよっかな？"
